  "description": "<b>为了给即将开幕的E3 2013游戏展，EA举办了一场自己的发布会，期间首次进行了《极品飞车：宿敌》（Need for Speed：Rivals）的实机演示，该游戏将在今年11月19日率先登陆PC、Xbox 360和PS3平台。</b>从现场视频内容来看，基于寒霜3（Frostbite 3）打造的《极品飞车：宿敌》拥有动态天气系统，游戏内比赛依旧采用了开放式的触发机制，同时允许两名玩家在同一场比赛中分别扮演地下飙车党和警察两种角色展开角力。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d1c01fb/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240706.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E3%80%8A%E6%9E%81%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9E%E8%BD%A618%E3%80%8B%E6%96%B0%E9%A2%84%E5%91%8A%2B%E9%A6%96%E6%AE%B5%E5%AE%9E%E6%9C%BA%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240706.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E3%80%8A%E6%9E%81%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9E%E8%BD%A618%E3%80%8B%E6%96%B0%E9%A2%84%E5%91%8A%2B%E9%A6%96%E6%AE%B5%E5%AE%9E%E6%9C%BA%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240706.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E3%80%8A%E6%9E%81%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9E%E8%BD%A618%E3%80%8B%E6%96%B0%E9%A2%84%E5%91%8A%2B%E9%A6%96%E6%AE%B5%E5%AE%9E%E6%9C%BA%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240706.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E3%80%8A%E6%9E%81%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9E%E8%BD%A618%E3%80%8B%E6%96%B0%E9%A2%84%E5%91%8A%2B%E9%A6%96%E6%AE%B5%E5%AE%9E%E6%9C%BA%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank